{"tid":2008319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【旅遊洋蔥】菲律賓男童乞討食物 取餐後跑走餵幼妹","createTime":"2020-05-09T03:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:57:14.000Z","uid":326037,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6e21e340d6707d1ce980ce0ced48724f3922cb","tid":2008319,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"【旅遊洋蔥】菲律賓男童乞討食物 取餐後跑走餵幼妹<br />\n<br />\n據菲律賓統計署去年的數據顯，菲律賓人口約 1 億 700 萬，當中約有 2200 萬人仍生活在貧窮線下。在菲律賓首都馬尼拉常常可以看到那些因為家裡貧困而失學的小孩，他們為了生活必須到街上打工或乞討。早前網上流傳了一個故事，指一對外國情侶遊菲律賓時，遇到一名乞討食物的男孩，男孩取餐後卻不是自己吃，而是跑回去餵自己年幼的妹妹。<br />\n<br />\n據說事件於 2016 年 12 月發生，當時外國情侶 Geo Tolentino Roger 和 John Benedict Ringor 正在菲律賓馬尼拉旅遊，遇到一個小男孩向他們乞討。Geo 和 John 同情小男孩的處境，於是走進附近的快餐連鎖店 Jollibee，買了一份套餐給小男孩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小男孩在拿到食物後立即跑走，本來也沒什麼稀奇，但該對情侶後來又在路上碰到這名男孩，他跟另一位小女孩在一起，原來這是他的妹妹，小男孩拿著剛剛他們給他的餐點，餵著妹妹吃飯。這對情侶將看到的景象拍了下來，後來上傳到網路上，並引來不少網民分享。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2635000/2636003/20190808085437619_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2635000%2F2636003%2F20190808085437619_1024.jpg&h=768a384d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2636003/%E3%80%90%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%B4%8B%E8%94%A5%E3%80%91%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E4%B9%9E%E8%A8%8E%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%20%E5%8F%96%E9%A4%90%E5%BE%8C%E8%B7%91%E8%B5%B0%E9%A4%B5%E5%B9%BC%E5%A6%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2636003%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25B4%258B%25E8%2594%25A5%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25B3%2593%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E4%25B9%259E%25E8%25A8%258E%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%2520%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25B7%2591%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E9%25A4%25B5%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E5%25A6%25B9&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=5532b35f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2636003/%E3%80%90%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%B4%8B%E8%94%A5%E3%80%91%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E4%B9%9E%E8%A8%8E%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%20%E5%8F%96%E9%A4%90%E5%BE%8C%E8%B7%91%E8%B5%B0%E9%A4%B5%E5%B9%BC%E5%A6%B9</a>"},{"pid":"fb793f3d8295508ef1729646331df0fde6e11c7d","tid":2008319,"uid":326037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"Geo和 John把這對兄妹的照片分享到網路上，引起了激烈迴響，許多網友為小男孩寧可沒吃飽也要讓妹妹飽餐一頓感動不已。不少富有的家庭在金錢的誘惑下發生矛盾、甚至因此反目，但這對兄妹卻沒有因為貧窮而拋下彼此，這份親情實在是難能可貴！"},{"pid":"f7bd49b43211a5ab4c72397d05fe65b36bfda2e9","tid":2008319,"uid":326037,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人口太多 生仔要考牌<br />\n窮人生仔正仆街</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5hBZM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5hBZM9.png&h=7aa5defb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"484d5fc41005ae2a33f76c46e8cf2cbad62069cb","tid":2008319,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba8cada5caed478518be4c4bab6b939143bc93d","tid":2008319,"uid":10572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"How dare you"},{"pid":"8a66f65bac224812ff9270d256d6b8db96038508","tid":2008319,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aba8cada5caed478518be4c4bab6b939143bc93d","tid":2008319,"uid":10572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"How dare you"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"359a61728759429b2ba72cbb3476765316e75bf4","tid":2008319,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"窮人真係咪生仔"}]}